00:20.228 --> 00:22.063
READ YOUR CONTRACT, GEOFFREY.

00:22.105 --> 00:24.191
ANYTHING YOU WORK ON

00:22.105 --> 00:24.191
AT FLUID DYN

00:24.232 --> 00:25.526
IS OWNED BY FLUID DYN.

