THAT'S A HOBBY PROJECT, I SWEAR.

00:28.236 --> 00:29.363
I ONLY WORK ON THAT AT HOME.

00:29.404 --> 00:31.114
THIS IS SOME

00:29.404 --> 00:31.114
PRETTY SOPHISTICATED STUFF.

00:31.156 --> 00:32.867
DO YOU REALLY EXPECT

00:31.156 --> 00:32.867
ANYONE TO BELIEVE

00:32.908 --> 00:35.327
THAT YOU WORKED ON THIS OVER

00:32.908 --> 00:35.327
THE WEEKEND IN YOUR UNDERWEAR?

00:35.369 --> 00:37.037
I DIDN'T DO IT

00:35.369 --> 00:37.037
IN A WEEKEND, JOHN.

00:37.078 --> 00:39.540
