00:37.078 --> 00:39.540
IN 10 YEARS' WORTH OF WEEKENDS.

00:39.581 --> 00:41.876
WHILE YOU WERE GETTING MARRIED

00:39.581 --> 00:41.876
AND HAVING A KID,

00:41.917 --> 00:44.378
I WAS ALONE IN MY GARAGE,

00:41.917 --> 00:44.378
TRYING TO CHANGE THE WORLD.

00:44.419 --> 00:46.922
YOU HAVE NO IDEA WHAT YOU HAVE

00:44.419 --> 00:46.922
IN YOUR HANDS RIGHT NOW.

00:46.964 --> 00:50.009
IF THAT WERE TRUE, DO

00:46.964 --> 00:50.009
YOU REALLY THINK THIS

00:46.964 --> 00:50.009
WOULD BE HAPPENING?

00:51.552 --> 00:53.554
SON OF A BITCH!

00:53.595 --> 00:55.597
OH, AND...YOU'RE FIRED.

00:55.639 --> 00:57.766
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

00:55.639 --> 00:57.766
HEY, WHAT -- GET OFF ME.

00:57.808 --> 01:00.019
HEY! GET YOUR HANDS OFF ME!

01:00.060 --> 01:02.855
THE RICH AND POWERFUL

01:00.060 --> 01:02.855
TAKE WHAT THEY WANT.

01:02.897 --> 01:04.899
WE STEAL IT BACK FOR YOU.

01:11.697 --> 01:15.826
SOMETIMES, BAD GUYS

01:11.697 --> 01:15.826
MAKE THE BEST GOOD GUYS.

01:17.494 --> 01:18.787
WE PROVIDE...

01:20.080 --> 01:22.374
WHAT DOES THIS CHIP DO, EXACTLY?

01:22.416 --> 01:23.584
IT'S NOT WHAT. IT'S HOW.

01:23.625 --> 01:25.126
THE SIMPLE VERSION IS THAT

01:25.168 --> 01:27.170
IT'S AN ENVIRONMENTALLY ADAPTIVE

01:25.168 --> 01:27.170
DESIGN THAT MAXIMIZES TTF --

01:27.212 --> 01:29.048
TIME TO FAILURE --

01:27.212 --> 01:29.048
ON INTEGRATED CIRCUITS.

01:29.088 --> 01:31.383
THAT'S THE SIMPLE VERSION?

01:31.425 --> 01:32.467
I'M SORRY.

01:32.509 --> 01:35.303
BASICALLY, IT --

01:32.509 --> 01:35.303
IT CHANGES EVERYTHING.

01:35.345 --> 01:36.931
WHAT ABOUT

01:35.345 --> 01:36.931
MILITARY APPLICATIONS?

01:36.972 --> 01:38.807
EVERYTHING

01:36.972 --> 01:38.807
THAT A COMPUTER CAN DO,

01:38.849 --> 01:41.309
MY DESIGN CAN DO IT

01:38.849 --> 01:41.309
FASTER, BETTER, AND CHEAPER.

01:41.351 --> 01:44.271
BUT HOW DO THEY PLAN

01:41.351 --> 01:44.271
TO FABRICATE DESIGN HISTORY?

01:44.312 --> 01:45.898
THAT'S WHAT NEVER MADE SENSE.

01:45.940 --> 01:47.733
YOU CAN'T BRING A CHIP TO MARKET

01:45.940 --> 01:47.733
WITHOUT AN R&D TRAIL, SO I SUED,

01:47.775 --> 01:49.026
AND THAT'S WHEN CONNELL

01:47.775 --> 01:49.026
DID SOMETHING

01:49.068 --> 01:50.444
I WOULDN'T HAVE GUESSED

01:49.068 --> 01:50.444
IN A MILLION YEARS.

01:50.485 --> 01:52.112
WHAT'S THAT?

01:52.153 --> 01:53.530
HE LIED. NO, HE LIED.

01:53.572 --> 01:55.449
HIS STORY

01:53.572 --> 01:55.449
IS THAT GEOFFREY ATTACKED HIM

01:55.490 --> 01:57.409
AFTER BEING PASSED OVER

01:55.490 --> 01:57.409
ON A PROMOTION.

01:57.451 --> 01:59.286
NOW, IN HIS VERSION,

01:57.451 --> 01:59.286
THERE IS NO CHIP.

01:59.327 --> 02:00.704
HMM. WELL, IT MAKES SENSE.

02:00.746 --> 02:02.456
WHY WOULD HE

02:00.746 --> 02:02.456
ADMIT TO STEALING IT?

02:02.497 --> 02:04.792
WELL, BECAUSE IT'S THE BASIS

02:02.497 --> 02:04.792
FOR THE LEGAL CLAIM.

02:04.833 --> 02:06.251
DENYING IT EVER HAPPENED

02:06.293 --> 02:08.503
FORFEITS ANY RIGHTS FLUID DYN

02:06.293 --> 02:08.503
WOULD HAVE ON THE DESIGN.

02:08.545 --> 02:09.922
WHY WOULD HE DO THAT?

02:09.964 --> 02:11.465
BECAUSE HE DIDN'T STEAL IT

02:09.964 --> 02:11.465
FOR FLUID DYN.

02:11.506 --> 02:13.008
-HE STOLE IT FOR HIMSELF.

02:11.506 --> 02:13.008
-IT'S BLACK MARKET.

02:13.050 --> 02:15.385
WELL, THAT EXPLAINS

02:13.050 --> 02:15.385
CONNELL'S TRIPS TO RUSSIA

02:15.427 --> 02:16.971
OVER THE LAST THREE MONTHS.

02:17.012 --> 02:18.221
HARDISON?

02:23.184 --> 02:24.770
THERE'S YOUR LIVE FEED

02:23.184 --> 02:24.770
FROM CONNELL'S HOUSE,

02:24.812 --> 02:25.854
brought to you by Lucille.

02:25.896 --> 02:27.982
So now what she sees,

02:25.896 --> 02:27.982
you all see.

02:28.023 --> 02:30.358
OOH, NICE HOUSE

02:28.023 --> 02:30.358
FOR A V.P. OF SALES.

02:30.400 --> 02:32.778
YEAH, WELL, HE --

02:30.400 --> 02:32.778
