How many times did I tell you

02:51.046 --> 02:53.507
not to use that word around me?

02:53.548 --> 02:55.216
That's easy for you to say,

02:55.258 --> 02:57.970
but I'm the one who loses his

02:55.258 --> 02:57.970
license if you get inspected.

02:58.012 --> 02:59.513
Come on, man. It's never been

02:58.012 --> 02:59.513
a problem before.

