03:02.808 --> 03:04.559
My George Washington report?

03:04.601 --> 03:06.812
-THAT'S HIS DAUGHTER, MOLLY.

03:04.601 --> 03:06.812
-I'm fine fudging a line

03:04.601 --> 03:06.812
here and there,

03:06.854 --> 03:08.271
