03:11.399 --> 03:14.193
Cherry tree, ax, chop-chop.

03:14.235 --> 03:16.321
Anyway, so,

03:14.235 --> 03:16.321
I can use your computer?

03:16.363 --> 03:19.449
-[ Russian accent ] Molly!

03:16.363 --> 03:19.449
-Daria. Daria, where

03:16.363 --> 03:19.449
have you been?

03:19.491 --> 03:20.868
-THAT'S THE NANNY.

03:19.491 --> 03:20.868
-Never mind.

03:20.909 --> 03:22.119
Come on. Get up here.

03:22.161 --> 03:23.704
-[ Sighs ] Forget it.

03:22.161 --> 03:23.704
-Where have you been?

03:23.745 --> 03:25.998
I'll just be the only kid

03:23.745 --> 03:25.998
