03:26.040 --> 03:27.833
THAT'S ENOUGH.

03:27.875 --> 03:29.501
WHERE'S THE MOTHER IN ALL THIS?

03:29.543 --> 03:31.210
ACCORDING TO...

03:31.252 --> 03:32.671
DEAD.

03:32.713 --> 03:34.006
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

03:34.048 --> 03:36.216
YEAH, UH, SHE DIED A YEAR AGO.

03:36.257 --> 03:37.342
HOW DID YOU --

03:37.384 --> 03:38.593
IT'S THE WAY HE LOOKS AT MOLLY.

03:38.635 --> 03:39.845
HE LOVES HER, BUT ALSO,

03:39.887 --> 03:43.264
SHE REMINDS HIM

03:39.887 --> 03:43.264
OF SOMETHING THAT HE'S LOST.

03:43.306 --> 03:45.559
WELL, THAT EXPLAINS

03:43.306 --> 03:45.559
HIS FOCUS ON THE HOUSE.

03:45.600 --> 03:47.310
HE'S COMPENSATING FOR HIS LOSS

03:47.352 --> 03:49.563
BY EXERTING POWER

03:47.352 --> 03:49.563
OVER HIS WORLD.

03:49.604 --> 03:52.524
HARDISON, CAN YOU BRING UP

03:49.604 --> 03:52.524
THE BLUEPRINT ON THE HOUSE?

03:52.566 --> 03:55.194
SO, YOU'RE SAYING

03:52.566 --> 03:55.194
THAT BEING $1 MILLION IN DEBT --

03:55.235 --> 03:56.528
THAT'S A LOT OF CONTROL?

03:56.570 --> 03:58.947
WELL, IT PROBABLY

03:56.570 --> 03:58.947
DOESN'T EVEN REGISTER.

03:58.989 --> 04:02.076
I MEAN, THAT'S NOT GREED

03:58.989 --> 04:02.076
WE'RE LOOKING AT IT. IT'S GRIEF.

04:02.117 --> 04:05.662
I THOUGHT WE WERE SUPPOSED TO

04:02.117 --> 04:05.662
HATE THE GUYS THAT WE TAKE DOWN.

04:05.704 --> 04:07.539
NOT A REQUIREMENT -- A PERK...

04:07.581 --> 04:08.540
USUALLY.

04:08.582 --> 04:09.917
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

04:09.958 --> 04:12.794
OKAY, SO, WE ARE HERE

04:09.958 --> 04:12.794
TO GET GEOFFREY'S CHIP BACK.

04:12.836 --> 04:15.296
NOW, I HAVE NO DOUBT

04:12.836 --> 04:15.296
IT'S IN THAT HOUSE SOMEWHERE.

04:15.338 --> 04:17.132
I JUST -- I DON'T KNOW WHERE.

04:17.174 --> 04:18.717
LOOK FOR A ROOM OR A DOOR

04:18.759 --> 04:21.095
THAT DOESN'T GO

04:18.759 --> 04:21.095
WITH THE REST OF THE HOUSE.

04:21.136 --> 04:23.097
SO, HOW DO YOU

04:21.136 --> 04:23.097
WANT TO GET INSIDE?

04:23.138 --> 04:26.558
OH, I THOUGHT WE'D JUST, YOU

04:23.138 --> 04:26.558
KNOW, WAIT FOR AN INVITATION.

