[ CLICKING ]

04:31.479 --> 04:33.774
[ NATE WHISTLING ]

04:33.815 --> 04:35.650
[ HORN HONKING ]

04:38.319 --> 04:40.280
LADY, COME ON.

04:38.319 --> 04:40.280
I GOT TO GET TO MY HOUSE.

04:40.321 --> 04:41.281
AH!

04:41.322 --> 04:42.741
LET ME ASK YOU A QUESTION --

04:42.783 --> 04:45.077
HOW DO YOU FEEL ABOUT LIVING

04:42.783 --> 04:45.077
IN THE SHADE OF GREATNESS?

04:45.119 --> 04:46.787
SHADOW -- SHE WANTS YOU

04:45.119 --> 04:46.787
TO LIVE IN THE SHADOW.

04:46.828 --> 04:49.081
SHADE, SHADOW,

04:46.828 --> 04:49.081
"TOMAHTO," "TOMAHTO."

04:46.828 --> 04:49.081
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

