04:54.211 --> 04:55.170
BECKA JESSUP.

04:55.212 --> 04:56.337
CONTRACTORS.

04:56.379 --> 04:58.799
YOU KNOW WHAT I'M THINKING

04:56.379 --> 04:58.799
THAT HOUSE NEEDS

04:58.840 --> 05:00.717
-TO ACHIEVE ITS POTENTIAL

04:58.840 --> 05:00.717
FOR GREATNESS?

04:58.840 --> 05:00.717
-WHAT? YEAH?

05:00.759 --> 05:02.136
-A SPIRE.

