I HOPE YOU LIKE ASPHALT, BUDDY.

05:12.187 --> 05:13.647
YEAH.

05:12.187 --> 05:13.647
I-I HOPE YOU LIKE ASPHALT.

05:13.688 --> 05:16.984
DEAR, DEAR, DEAR. YOUR

05:13.688 --> 05:16.984
LANDSCAPING'S GONNA HAVE TO GO.

05:17.025 --> 05:19.236
NOT ENOUGH SUNLIGHT,

05:17.025 --> 05:19.236
YOU UNDERSTAND.

05:19.278 --> 05:22.405
LOOK -- I-I DON'T KNOW

05:19.278 --> 05:22.405
