08:14.244 --> 08:16.537
A CCTV IN THERE, YOU KNOW,

08:16.579 --> 08:18.332
IT'D BE EASY

08:16.579 --> 08:18.332
FOR HIM TO WIRE THE --

08:18.373 --> 08:19.374
NOBODY GOES IN.

