29:23.637 --> 29:25.931
-[ SCOFFS ]

29:25.972 --> 29:28.559
WHERE I COME FROM,

29:25.972 --> 29:28.559
BOSS IS THE GUY WITH THE GUN.

29:28.601 --> 29:31.478
YEAH, WELL, IN AMERICA, THE BOSS

29:28.601 --> 29:31.478
IS THE GUY WHO DOESN'T NEED

29:28.601 --> 29:31.478
A GUN.

29:31.520 --> 29:33.021
YOU KNOW, HERE'S THE THING --

29:33.063 --> 29:34.732
IF YOU HAD PERMISSION

29:33.063 --> 29:34.732
TO PULL THAT THING,

29:34.814 --> 29:36.191
I THINK YOU WOULD HAVE

29:34.814 --> 29:36.191
DONE IT ALREADY.

29:36.233 --> 29:37.443
LITTLE RESPECT!

29:37.484 --> 29:39.612
THAT'S ALL I'M ASKING FOR --

29:37.484 --> 29:39.612
COMMON COURTESY!

29:39.653 --> 29:40.987
THERE IS NOBODY HERE BUT US.

29:41.029 --> 29:43.073
LOOK, I HAVEN'T

29:41.029 --> 29:43.073
MADE MYSELF CLEAR, HAVE I?

29:43.115 --> 29:46.076
I'M GONNA SPEAK TO NO ONE

29:43.115 --> 29:46.076
BUT HER.

29:46.118 --> 29:48.495
HOW DID YOU KNOW?

29:52.374 --> 29:53.333
OH! LOOK.

29:53.375 --> 29:56.128
IT'S YOUR FATHER CALLING.

29:56.169 --> 29:58.589
HE SAY WE MUST GO NOW

29:56.169 --> 29:58.589
OR WE'LL BE LATE.

29:58.631 --> 30:00.799
-NOT SO HARD.

29:58.631 --> 30:00.799
-HOLY CRAP.

30:00.840 --> 30:02.426
I QUIT! HA!

30:03.427 --> 30:05.721
-WHAT WAS THAT ABOUT?

30:03.427 --> 30:05.721
-[ SIGHS ]

30:05.763 --> 30:08.641
BETTER GO GET HER.

30:08.682 --> 30:10.517
[ CELLPHONE BEEPING ]

30:12.311 --> 30:14.730
I DON'T THINK THAT MR. CONNELL

30:12.311 --> 30:14.730
WANTS ANYONE BACK HERE.

30:17.899 --> 30:18.817
THANKS.

30:21.695 --> 30:23.447
LUCKY GUESS.

30:24.698 --> 30:26.116
OKAY, PARKER.

30:26.158 --> 30:28.494
PARKER, IT'S ON. GET THERE.

30:35.125 --> 30:36.669
WHERE'S MOLLY?

30:36.710 --> 30:38.295
SAFE.

30:38.337 --> 30:41.507
THIS NEGOTIATION WON'T BEGIN

30:38.337 --> 30:41.507
UNTIL YOU GIVE ME PROOF.

30:41.548 --> 30:46.219
YOU SHOULD LOOK AT YOUR CHEST

30:41.548 --> 30:46.219
BEFORE MAKING ANY MORE DEMANDS.

31:10.952 --> 31:14.164
I'D LIKE TO SEE

31:10.952 --> 31:14.164
PARKER 2000 TRY  THAT.

31:14.206 --> 31:15.582
Eliot?

31:16.875 --> 31:18.960
ELIOT?

31:19.002 --> 31:20.587
YOU OKAY?

31:22.506 --> 31:25.592
Eliot?

31:25.634 --> 31:26.593
Eliot?

31:26.635 --> 31:28.512
MOLLY, MY NAME'S SOPHIE.

31:28.554 --> 31:29.763
I'm looking out for you.

31:29.805 --> 31:32.140
Everything's

31:29.805 --> 31:32.140
gonna be fine, Molly.

31:32.182 --> 31:33.975
MOLLY, CAN YOU HEAR --

31:34.017 --> 31:35.811
SHE'S MY DAUGHTER.

31:41.859 --> 31:42.942
MOLLY?

31:42.984 --> 31:44.986
DAD?

31:45.028 --> 31:47.030
-Dad?

31:45.028 --> 31:47.030
-[ CLEARS THROAT ]

31:47.072 --> 31:51.410
[ Voice breaking ] HONEY,

31:47.072 --> 31:51.410
EVERYTHING'S GOING ACCORDING

31:47.072 --> 31:51.410
TO PLAN, UM...

31:51.451 --> 31:53.995
HEY, YOU KNOW THAT I ONLY

31:51.451 --> 31:53.995
HIRE THE BEST, RIGHT?

31:54.037 --> 31:55.455
YEAH.

31:55.497 --> 31:59.000
WELL, THAT'S WHO'S

31:55.497 --> 31:59.000
COMING TO GET YOU -- THE BEST.

31:59.042 --> 32:01.378
AND THEY'RE GONNA BRING YOU BACK

31:59.042 --> 32:01.378
SAFE AND SOUND,

32:01.420 --> 32:02.838
AND I'LL BE RIGHT HERE, WAITING.

32:05.006 --> 32:07.300
I'LL BE HERE FOR YOU, MOLLY.

32:07.342 --> 32:10.303
FROM NOW ON, I PROMISE --

32:07.342 --> 32:10.303
JUST YOU AND ME.

32:10.345 --> 32:12.639
I WISH I WAS WITH YOU

32:10.345 --> 32:12.639
RIGHT NOW, DAD.

32:15.934 --> 32:17.561
ME TOO, HONEY.

32:17.603 --> 32:20.272
YOU JUST HANG ON

32:17.603 --> 32:20.272
A LITTLE BIT LONGER,

32:20.313 --> 32:23.191
AND WE'LL BOTH SEE EACH OTHER

32:20.313 --> 32:23.191
REAL SOON, OKAY?

32:25.444 --> 32:27.279
MOLLY...

32:27.320 --> 32:29.573
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

32:29.615 --> 32:31.867
[ Voice breaking ]

32:29.615 --> 32:31.867
I LOVE YOU, TOO, DADDY.

32:34.787 --> 32:36.371
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

32:36.413 --> 32:38.957
YOU DID GOOD.

32:38.998 --> 32:42.252
Eliot? Eliot?

32:44.003 --> 32:45.881
Are you at the storage shed?

32:47.674 --> 32:49.718
Eliot, did you find Molly?

32:49.760 --> 32:50.928
Eliot?

32:57.267 --> 33:00.646
IF YOU KILL ME,

32:57.267 --> 33:00.646
HOW WILL YOU FIND THE GIRL?

33:00.687 --> 33:02.397
ACTUALLY, I WAS GONNA DO IT

33:00.687 --> 33:02.397
THE OTHER WAY AROUND.

33:02.439 --> 33:05.609
OH, SO YOU KNOW

33:02.439 --> 33:05.609
WHERE SHE IS, THEN?

33:08.987 --> 33:10.823
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

33:16.453 --> 33:19.247
SHE'S NOT -- SHE'S NOT HERE.

33:19.289 --> 33:21.374
Nate, they moved her.

33:32.218 --> 33:35.722
Best move for you

33:32.218 --> 33:35.722
is just to hand her over.

33:35.764 --> 33:37.766
ONCE I AM SAFE WITH CHIP,

33:35.764 --> 33:37.766
YOU GET MOLLY.

33:37.808 --> 33:39.977
FIRST WE NEED PROOF OF LIFE.

33:40.018 --> 33:42.521
YOU THINK I HURT HER?

33:42.562 --> 33:45.858
[ Chuckling ] I RAISED HER --

33:42.562 --> 33:45.858
MORE THAN MR. CONNELL.

33:45.899 --> 33:48.485
You're gonna be in big trouble

33:45.899 --> 33:48.485
when they find me.

33:48.527 --> 33:51.070
-I said shut up.

33:48.527 --> 33:51.070
-MOLLY.

33:51.112 --> 33:52.322
MOLLY?

33:52.364 --> 33:56.326
YOU'RE GONNA REGRET THIS.

33:56.368 --> 33:58.203
SHUT UP.

33:58.244 --> 34:00.539
I'M HERE, BOTASKY.

34:00.580 --> 34:01.957
Give me a clue.

34:01.999 --> 34:03.834
I DON'T LIKE WHAT I SEE.

34:07.379 --> 34:10.173
MIRRORS AND I AREN'T EXACTLY

34:07.379 --> 34:10.173
ON SPEAKING TERMS.

34:10.215 --> 34:11.257
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

34:11.299 --> 34:13.134
I JUST DON'T LIKE WHAT I SEE.

34:29.401 --> 34:30.819
[ SPEAKS RUSSIAN ]

34:33.989 --> 34:36.575
NATE, I KNOW WHERE SHE'S AT.

34:33.989 --> 34:36.575
I'M GONNA GO GET HER.

34:36.616 --> 34:38.702
NO, ELIOT, DARIA'S GOT THE CHIP.

34:38.744 --> 34:40.078
WE GOT TO JUST WAI--

34:40.119 --> 34:41.788
I DON'T WAIT.

34:41.830 --> 34:43.957
I'M COMING FOR YOU, MOLLY.

34:47.627 --> 34:48.628
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

34:56.053 --> 34:57.804
ROPER.

34:58.722 --> 34:59.472
[ Echoing ] ELIOT!

34:59.514 --> 35:02.225
[ ROPER LAUGHS ]

35:02.267 --> 35:04.895
ELIOT, HELP ME. PLEASE!

35:04.937 --> 35:06.063
ARE YOU STILL THERE?

35:08.565 --> 35:10.316
ELIOT, I'M SCARED.

35:17.407 --> 35:19.743
[ ROPER LAUGHS ]

35:25.665 --> 35:29.210
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

35:29.252 --> 35:30.754
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

35:43.016 --> 35:44.517
PLEASE HELP ME.

35:44.559 --> 35:46.227
I'M SCARED.

35:46.269 --> 35:48.146
PLEASE.

36:20.929 --> 36:23.473
THE GREAT ELIOT SPENCER.

36:23.515 --> 36:25.350
[ LAUGHS ]

36:30.981 --> 36:33.859
IT'S DARK.

36:30.981 --> 36:33.859
I CAN'T SEE ANYTHING.

36:33.900 --> 36:36.153
ELIOT, I'M SCARED.

36:36.194 --> 36:37.904
GET UP, SPENCER.

36:45.286 --> 36:47.164
I DON'T LIKE WHAT I SEE.

36:47.205 --> 36:49.290
I'M SCARED.

37:38.006 --> 37:39.841
[ MUFFLED SCREAMING ]

37:45.931 --> 37:48.183
[ SOBBING ]

38:02.948 --> 38:04.407
MOLLY!

38:04.449 --> 38:06.993
MOLLY!

38:07.035 --> 38:08.494
MOLLY!

38:11.873 --> 38:13.499
DADDY!

38:14.667 --> 38:16.836
NICE WORK, PERKY.

38:16.878 --> 38:18.713
YOU TOO, BOTASKY.

38:28.514 --> 38:30.892
[ ALARM BEEPING ]

38:32.852 --> 38:34.520
[ ENGINE SPUTTERING ]

38:44.447 --> 38:45.824
[ Muffled ] SON OF A BITCH!

38:45.865 --> 38:47.742
LET ME OUT OF THIS CAR

38:45.865 --> 38:47.742
RIGHT NOW, YOU SON OF A BITCH!

38:47.784 --> 38:49.786
-SORRY, WHAT? I CAN'T HEAR YOU.

38:47.784 --> 38:49.786
-I WILL KILL YOU!

38:49.828 --> 38:51.496
-DO YOU HEAR ME? I WILL --

38:49.828 --> 38:51.496
-YOU'LL WHAT?

38:51.537 --> 38:54.874
EVERYTHING IN YOUR LIFE OPERATES

38:51.537 --> 38:54.874
OFF THIS GUY RIGHT HERE --

38:54.916 --> 38:57.127
YOUR LOCKS, YOUR VIDEO CAMERAS,

38:57.169 --> 38:59.129
OR I COULD WIRE IT

38:57.169 --> 38:59.129
TO YOUR VEHICLE.

38:59.171 --> 39:01.923
YOU CAN, LIKE, START YOUR CAR

38:59.171 --> 39:01.923
OR PLAY A PARTICULAR CD,

39:01.965 --> 39:03.633
LOCK, UNLOCK THE DOORS,

39:01.965 --> 39:03.633
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

39:03.675 --> 39:05.093
IT'S PRETTY FREAKIN'

39:03.675 --> 39:05.093
SWEET, SO...

39:11.891 --> 39:14.269
[ ENGINE CLICKING ]

39:14.311 --> 39:16.354
[ ENGINE STOPS ]

39:16.395 --> 39:18.982
[ ENGINE SPUTTERS ]

39:19.024 --> 39:20.984
-LET ME OUT!

39:19.024 --> 39:20.984
-I'M SORRY. WHAT?

39:21.026 --> 39:22.735
-LET ME OUT!

39:21.026 --> 39:22.735
-CAN'T HEAR YOU.

39:22.777 --> 39:24.362
I WILL KILL YOU!

39:24.403 --> 39:25.780
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO!

39:25.822 --> 39:27.532
NO, WAIT! WAIT!

39:27.573 --> 39:30.535
THIS IS NOT OVER!

39:30.576 --> 39:31.786
[ SIREN WAILS ]

39:31.828 --> 39:32.996
STOP! STOP!

39:36.749 --> 39:39.961
I CAN'T THANK YOU ENOUGH.

39:36.749 --> 39:39.961
THIS IS MY LIFE.

39:40.003 --> 39:41.880
AND IT SOUNDS LIKE CONNELL'S

39:40.003 --> 39:41.880
TURNED OVER A NEW LEAF.

39:41.921 --> 39:44.299
WELL, I WOULDN'T SAY

39:41.921 --> 39:44.299
"TURNED OVER A NEW

39:41.921 --> 39:44.299
LEAF" SO MUCH AS --

39:44.341 --> 39:45.842
OH, YOU KNOW,

39:44.341 --> 39:45.842
SOMETIMES, WHEN YOU LOSE

39:45.884 --> 39:47.969
SOMETHING THAT'S IMPORTANT,

39:45.884 --> 39:47.969
SOMETHING THAT CENTERS YOU,

39:48.011 --> 39:49.846
SOMETHING THAT YOU FEEL

39:48.011 --> 39:49.846
YOU CAN'T LIVE WITHOUT,

39:49.888 --> 39:51.139
YOU LOSE HOW TO LIVE.

39:51.181 --> 39:52.182
LIKE MY CHIP.

39:53.766 --> 39:55.143
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

39:56.895 --> 39:59.731
WELL, IT SOUNDS LIKE MOLLY

39:56.895 --> 39:59.731
AND HER DAD ARE DOING OKAY.

39:59.772 --> 40:01.566
THEY'RE MAKING UP FOR LOST TIME.

40:01.607 --> 40:04.819
HEY, MAN, YOU REALLY SHOULD HAVE

40:01.607 --> 40:04.819
LET US GET YOU TO A HOSPITAL.

40:04.861 --> 40:07.072
-I HIRED A NURSE.

40:04.861 --> 40:07.072
-AH, THATABOY.

40:07.113 --> 40:09.741
A LITTLE CHICKEN NOODLE SOUP,

40:07.113 --> 40:09.741
A LITTLE GRANDMOTHERLY LOVE.

40:09.782 --> 40:10.783
STOP.

40:15.288 --> 40:16.497
HEY. HOW ARE YOU?

40:16.539 --> 40:19.500
THIS IS NURSE GAIL.

40:21.127 --> 40:24.047
I DON'T THINK SHE'S REGISTERED.

40:25.757 --> 40:27.633
YOU DOING OKAY?

40:27.675 --> 40:29.677
ALWAYS.

40:34.266 --> 40:36.935
HOW YOU TWO DOING

40:34.266 --> 40:36.935
WITH YOUR LITTLE MINI-PARKER?

40:37.810 --> 40:40.063
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU

40:37.810 --> 40:40.063
BROUGHT HER HERE, BY THE WAY.

40:40.105 --> 40:42.065
OKAY, YOU KNOW WHAT, PARKER?

40:40.105 --> 40:42.065
LOOK.

40:42.107 --> 40:44.192
YOU WANT TO KNOW WHY

40:42.107 --> 40:44.192
I MADE IT GREEN?

40:44.234 --> 40:46.527
-MM-HMM.

40:44.234 --> 40:46.527
-BECAUSE YOUR FAVORITE COLOR

40:44.234 --> 40:46.527
IS GREEN.

40:46.569 --> 40:48.780
YOU WANT TO KNOW

40:46.569 --> 40:48.780
WHY I NAMED HER AFTER YOU?

40:48.821 --> 40:50.740
IT'S BECAUSE

40:48.821 --> 40:50.740
SHE'S BASED OFF OF YOU.

40:50.782 --> 40:52.367
PARKER, THAT'S WHY

40:50.782 --> 40:52.367
I WAS ALWAYS ASKING YOU,

40:52.409 --> 40:53.368
"WHAT ARE YOU THINKING?

40:53.410 --> 40:54.827
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?"

40:54.869 --> 40:57.914
EVERYTHING SHE KNOWS,

40:54.869 --> 40:57.914
SHE LEARNED OFF OF YOU.

40:57.956 --> 41:00.458
I DIDN'T MAKE HER

40:57.956 --> 41:00.458
TO REPLACE YOU.

41:00.499 --> 41:02.794
I'D NEVER WANT TO REPLACE YOU.

41:02.835 --> 41:06.589
SHE'S -- SHE'S  FOR  YOU.

41:11.510 --> 41:13.846
[ CHUCKLES ] I LOVE IT.

41:13.888 --> 41:14.889
REALLY?

41:14.931 --> 41:16.682
YEAH.

41:14.931 --> 41:16.682
I'M GONNA CALL HER "HARDY."

41:16.724 --> 41:19.811
OKAY. NO.

41:16.724 --> 41:19.811
UM, IT'S "PARKER 2000."

41:19.852 --> 41:22.021
-IT SAYS SO RIGHT THERE

41:19.852 --> 41:22.021
IN THE FINE PRINT.

41:19.852 --> 41:22.021
-IT USED TO BE.

41:22.063 --> 41:25.150
OKAY, NO. THAT'S --

41:22.063 --> 41:25.150
THAT'S NOT GONNA WORK.

41:25.191 --> 41:26.859
-THAT'S --

41:25.191 --> 41:26.859
-HARDY IT IS.

41:26.901 --> 41:29.070
BUT IT'S PARKER 2000.

41:26.901 --> 41:29.070
IT'S LIKE --

41:29.112 --> 41:31.072
YEAH, BUT YOU SAID IT'S MINE,

41:29.112 --> 41:31.072
SO I CAN NAME IT

41:29.112 --> 41:31.072
WHATEVER I WANT.

41:31.114 --> 41:33.074
SHE SHALL BE CALLED HARDY.

41:31.114 --> 41:33.074
YOU LIKE THAT NAME, DON'T YOU?

41:33.116 --> 41:34.909
[ High-pitched voice ] YES.

41:33.116 --> 41:34.909
[ Normal voice ] YES.

41:34.951 --> 41:37.829
RIGHT, BUT WHEN I INVENTED IT,

41:34.951 --> 41:37.829
I REGISTERED THE NAME

41:34.951 --> 41:37.829
AS PARKER 2000.

41:37.870 --> 41:40.373
-SHE LIKES IT. SHE LIKES IT.

41:37.870 --> 41:40.373
-HARDY IS GOOD. I CAN  MAKE

41:37.870 --> 41:40.373
A HARDY.
